<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Inventory App</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar", { links }) %>
    <main>
      <header>Home</header>
      <p>
        Welcome to Game Vault, your go-to hub for discovering and tracking video games! Our site offers a streamlined inventory filled with essential information about your favorite titles. Each entry includes the game title, price, a brief overview, release date, developer, genres, and platforms.
        <br>
        Whether you're hunting for the latest blockbuster or a hidden gem, Game Vault makes it easy to find what you need at a glance. Explore our collection to stay informed and make the best gaming choices! Join us as we celebrate the diverse world of video games, one title at a time. Happy gaming!
      </p>
      <ul>
        <h1>New additions</h1>
        <% games.forEach((game) => { %>
          <li>
            <p><%= game.game %></p>
            <p><%= game.price %>â‚¬</p>
            <p><%= game.developersString %></p>
            <p><%= game.genresString %></p>
            <p><%= game.platformsString %></p>
          </li>
        <% }) %>
      </ul>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>